scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 3-136 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE to the 2002 Master Agreement' and ending with '[Signature page to follow]'. The content includes all the negotiated terms and elections specific to the parties, which is the purpose of the Schedule. Lines before 3 are cover/identification, and lines after 136 are confirmations and annexes, not part of the Schedule.
